inlineContent.text: protocol in the object you use to coordinate changes in your web view’s main frame. As the user attempts to navigate web content, the web view coordinates with its navigation delegate to manage any transitions. For example, you might use these methods to restrict navigation from specific links within your content. You might also use them to track the progress of requests, and to respond to errors and authentication challenges.
